            <p>Version 4.2.4 (January 2021)</p>
            <p>Changes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Build fixes for MOE.Common and AsyncGetMaxTimeRecords. *Note: Test products have to be unloaded for solution to build</li>
                <Li>Remove SpmApi project - seems to have been replaced by AtspmApi project but was still referenced in sln file.</Li>
